headline: Insurance Stocks Gain Ground in Turbulent Markets. Boring Might Be the Way to Go.
summary: Insurance stocks are quietly outperforming, delivering steady gains as volatility rattles much of the broader market.  Through Thursday’s close, the stock is up 6% for the week, achieving its heaviest weekly volume in the past 10 months without even counting Friday’s session.
